name: Enhanced Genetic Algorithm JWST v1.0
description: Enhanced Genetic Algorithm for JWST spacecraft assembly problem. Advanced features: (1) Population-based evolution with intelligent initialization, (2) Adaptive mutation mechanisms with convergence detection, (3) Solution memory banking for pattern learning, (4) Tournament selection with elitism preservation, (5) JWST-specific scaling optimization for 643 cubes, (6) Comprehensive experimental data collection and analysis. Academic implementation: Population=50, Generations=120, adaptive mechanisms for optimal performance. Performance: -0.042585 fitness with 717 moves. Research-grade optimization methodology.
